title: Friend doesn't want to duo with you because you don't "carry" him...(You are higher tier/division)
body:
Proceeds to "solo" Q and went on a losing streak, then uninstalled.

"why you play without me, we can just duo and win more" 

"w/e It's not like you ever carry me"

Sry, I don't get 15 kills per game, but I also don't die 10 times per game to kill supports.
